OL,4,Cand murdered gran released from jail
OL,6,FA teenager who tortured and murdered a
OL,7,Fgrandmother 26 years ago has been
OL,8,Freleased from prison.
OL,10,FSarah Davey, from Failsworth in
OL,11,FManchester, was just 14 when she and
OL,12,Fher 15-year-old friend Lisa Healey
OL,13,Fbefriended Lily Lilley and brutally
OL,14,Fmurdered her at the pensioner's home.
OL,16,FThe pair tortured the 71-year-old by
OL,17,Fsquirting shampoo in her eyes, cutting
OL,18,Fher with a knife and tying a gag round
OL,19,Fher mouth so tightly that her dentures
OL,20,Fwere forced down her throat at the
OL,21,Fhouse on West Street in Oldham.
