OL,6,FDavey and Healey then dumped her body
OL,7,Fin a bin and walked it through the
OL,8,Fstreets of Failsworth before throwing
OL,9,FLily in the Rochdale Canal.
OL,11,FAfter the killing, Davey and Healey
OL,12,Fmade hundreds of calls from her phone
OL,13,Fand used Lily's pension money to buy
OL,14,Fcrisps and chocolate.
OL,16,FIn 1999, Davey was handed an
OL,17,Findeterminate sentence by a judge who
OL,18,Fdescribed the murder as 'unspeakably
OL,19,Fwicked'.
