OL,6,FDavey, who is now in her late 30s, was
OL,7,Freleased from prison on 23 March 2024
OL,8,Fafter a decision by the Parole Board.
OL,10,FSince March 2013, Davey has been
OL,11,Freleased from prison on licence seven
OL,12,Ftimes.
OL,14,FIn 2013, she was freed from Askham
OL,15,FGrange women's prison near York after
OL,16,Fserving 14 years behind bars.
OL,18,FShe then moved back to Greater
OL,19,FManchester - and was living just two
OL,20,Fmiles from the scene of the killing.
