OL,6,FBut that same year she was behind bars
OL,7,Fagain after testing positive for using
OL,8,Fcocaine, breaching the terms of her
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FEach time she was released from prison
OL,12,Fafter that, she was recalled for
OL,13,Fbreaching the terms of her licence.
OL,15,FIn 2022, the Parole Board rejected
OL,16,FDavey's release for an eighth time.
OL,18,FAt a hearing, it was revealed that she
OL,19,Fhad the opioid painkiller subutex in
OL,20,Fher system.
