OL,6,FOn Davey's release earlier this year,
OL,7,Fthe Parole Board said she was allowed
OL,8,Fout following an oral hearing.
OL,10,FIn full, a spokesperson for the board
OL,11,Fsaid in a statement: "We can confirm
OL,12,Fthat a panel of the Parole Board has
OL,13,Fdirected the release of Sarah Davey
OL,14,Ffollowing an oral hearing.
OL,16,F"Parole Board decisions are solely
OL,17,Ffocused on what risk a prisoner could
OL,18,Frepresent to the public if released
OL,19,Fand whether that risk is manageable in
OL,20,Fthe community.
